    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car is totally ready for its next adventure. It's been well-loved and runs like a charm. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
