    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted driver\u2019s car featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. The longitudinal 6-speed manual transmission delivers power to a factory-spec limited-slip differential, ensuring exceptional corner-exit traction. Key preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a VANOS system refresh and essential rear subframe reinforcement to maintain torsional rigidity. The suspension geometry remains precise with upgraded trailing arm bushings, providing the tactile feedback and balance that defines this chassis. While it shows honest patina from spirited use, the drivetrain remains robust and the throttle response is razor-sharp. A true enthusiast-spec machine ready for the open road.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Runs well. Clean title. Minor cosmetic wear. No mechanical issues.",
