    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been exceptionally well-maintained and offers a fantastic balance of luxury and reliability. The exterior retains a beautiful shine, with only a few minor stone chips on the front bumper that are typical of careful road use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and has never been smoked in; the premium leather seats are supple, and the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. Every feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the premium sound system and heated seats, is in perfect working order. Mechanically, the car is in great shape with a full-service history documented at the dealership. It recently underwent a multi-point inspection, received a fresh oil change, and had the brake pads replaced. The tires have significant tread remaining, ensuring a smooth and safe ride for the new owner. This is a solid, dependable car that shows pride of ownership and is ready for the road today.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
