      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it the perfect choice for someone who wants a dependable daily driver that still looks great on the road. I\u2019ve kept up with the essentials, so it\u2019s all set for your next adventure. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
