    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, complete with individual throttle bodies and a recently serviced double VANOS system. This example utilizes the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox, sending power through a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. To ensure structural integrity, the rear subframe has been reinforced\u2014a critical preventative measure for this chassis. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics, and the rod bearing service has been documented. While showing minor road-rash and light interior patina indicative of its 'good' status, the vehicle remains a performance-first machine with a crisp throttle response and a linear power band that pulls hard to the 8,000 RPM redline.",
